ZH: 这个箱子很沉重，你需要帮忙吗？
EN: This box is very heavy, do you need help?

ZH: 这些沙袋很沉重，需要多人合力才能搬动。
EN: These sandbags are very heavy, it takes several people working together to move them.

ZH: 我感到心情沉重，不知道怎么办。
EN: I feel heavy-hearted and don't know what to do.

ZH: 那个书包里装了很多书，很沉重。
EN: The backpack is loaded with so many books, it is very heavy.

